The video clip showing hundreds of women: not related to the recent developments in Kashmir after article 370 was revoked.
The video was originally posted on YouTu: which is associated with the political party Pakistan Muslim League (Nawaz).
A banner seen in the video mentioned: Baramulla Central Cooperative Bank Ltd Branch, Hajin', indicating that the video was from Baramulla district in J&K.
A photograph of the funeral procession: similar to the video, was found on the stock photo site Alamy, further confirming its authenticity as a funeral procession rather than a women's march related to the revocation of article 370.
